s/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家啲小學都有教<br />\n唱下歌仔好易記"},{"pid":"6c66526f155ea78df221ec1e2eccce635be7bd77","tid":60524,"uid":71114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:17:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似永遠都發唔到岩既音 就好似pronunciation呢個字咁到而家都發唔得岩<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfWa7qzx9dENx6rsfbyruNWrZNCwyzQqP2oz2oGdnbFBR?filename=09TfY16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F09TfY16.jpg&h=c671094a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔識點打出黎  最頭個重音發到一舊屎咁<br />\n有無巴絲可以比啲意見我 學左咁多年英文 連r音th呢啲都發得唔好更加唔好講<br />\nfruit food<br />\nWill wheel <br />\n呢個對我黎講係分唔到咁制 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無人可以比啲建議我 或者交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇ipa夠唔夠熟？定估估下？<br />\n睇熟啲加查有聲字典啦，自己讀一次先，再禁發聲，睇下爭幾遠。<br />\n<br />\nFruit food分別好大喎，fruit有r音 t音，food冇。<br />\nWill同wheel 分別相對比較細，但都唔難聽。<br />\nWill聽落正常短好多，所以如果你聽得英文多會比較易分到，聽埋context 基本唔會錯。<br />\n<br />\nLL尾嘅字will/till/tall等等<br />\n睇開siu sir應該知，你讀啦啦啦啦啦，放到好慢讀，啦同啦中間你會發現你條利會係上排牙齒後面<br />\n呢個音就係LL尾嘅讀法<br />\n識讀自然識分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申讀過兩年書，塵世間一件迷途小書僮"},{"pid":"e534f53f35dc1c218d3db9171d0eb368ae08b03e","tid":60524,"uid":19178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T16:51:03.000Z","msg":"想問flash flesh<br />\n有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1964b7f82a2a1e6525aaaa23ce74537f50c69b18","tid":60524,"uid":63841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T16:54:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問flash flesh<br />\n有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係淨<br />\n啲啲，其實冇咩分別"},{"pid":"37e91771ca86d9c34cc92446cd07423ad18dd001","tid":60524,"uid":19178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T17:05:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問flash flesh<br />\n有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係淨<br />\n啲啲，其實冇咩分別</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"484c02aa3fb25bdb75f5a8fa64a7c296028be2e1","tid":60524,"uid":48729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T17:31:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問flash flesh<br />\n有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係淨<br />\n啲啲，其實冇咩分別</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n開口大細 / 舌位 都有啲唔同。 <br />\n我用 man men 做例子<br />\nman ，/&aelig;/ 音嚟嘅，要夾硬擘大啲個口<br />\nmen ，/e/ 音嚟，個嘴要細啲<br />\n<br />\n廣東話讀「咩」嗰個元音 &epsilon; 就喺兩個中間，所以要練習點分。"},{"pid":"330163732839a6b1fd350af9ec9bd8d744538b72","tid":60524,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:09:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇下啲兒童phonics教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家啲小學都有教<br />\n唱下歌仔好易記</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實唱呢個有乜野用？ 學節奏 ？真心唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c570e8748ca9bd9c5e8d95c69a8c7aa277182c","tid":60524,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:15:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好似永遠都發唔到岩既音 就好似pronunciation呢個字咁到而家都發唔得岩<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfWa7qzx9dENx6rsfbyruNWrZNCwyzQqP2oz2oGdnbFBR?filename=09TfY16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F09TfY16.jpg&h=c671094a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔識點打出黎